# --- Generated code (Avro codegen output) ---
# Per-service codegen is regenerated at build time and stays local.
**/generated/
**/__generated__/

# ...but the shared schema package commits its TS output on purpose, so a
# schema change shows up as a reviewable diff in the PR (ADR-0004 loudness).
!packages/schemas/generated/
!packages/schemas/generated/**

# --- Claude Code: track project skills, keep the rest of .claude/ local ---
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**
